## Correct ``lakebase_postgres_database`` default (schema vs DB)

Context: Default had been set to ``ontobricks_registry``, which is the
OntoBricks **schema** name, not the Lakebase Postgres **database**
(``datname``). The Apps binding must target the real DB (typically
``databricks_postgres``); the registry schema remains
``lakebase_registry_schema``.

Changes:

1. databricks.yml
   Default ``lakebase_postgres_database`` → ``databricks_postgres``; variable description clarifies DB vs schema; intro comment no longer assumes a single sandbox project id.

