## Lakebase Apps binding: ``db-…`` resource segment only

Context: Workspace API rejects ``…/databases/<datname>`` (e.g.
``databricks_postgres``). The path must end with the ``db-…`` segment
from ``list-databases`` ``name``. Replaced variable
``lakebase_postgres_database`` with ``lakebase_database_resource_segment``;
comments and README describe the CLI lookup. Default
``db-6ld8-ovemyuek1n`` matches ``status.postgres_database`` =
``databricks_postgres`` on project ``ontobricks-app`` / ``production``.

Changes:

1. databricks.yml
   Variable rename + accurate comments; postgres ``database`` path uses ``${var.lakebase_database_resource_segment}``.
2. README.md
   Lakebase deploy variables updated for the new name and lookup.
3. scripts/bootstrap-lakebase-perms.sh
   Comment references ``lakebase_database_resource_segment``.

